heory\nas well as with the Boundary Integral (BI) simulations in the potential flow\nlimit and the results are found to be in a reasonable agreement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Aug 2019 12:56:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Aug 2019 14:45:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2020 09:43:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
