of the A-core phase of\nrotating $^3$He-B, opening a window of stability down to low pressures. These\nresults are compared with the experimentally reported phase transitions in\nrotating $^3$He-B.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Aug 2019 15:12:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2020 03:39:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-11"}
